      DnD Spells is a website utilizing the Dungeons & Dragons Spell Listing dataset. This dataset is available for download in CSV format from the kaagle.com website.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="columns">
  <div class="column">
    <p>
      The purpose of this website is to display the contents of the dataset in an easily browsable format. The 
      dataset contains different columns: name, classes, level, school, cast_time, range, duration, verbal, somatic, 
      material, material_cost, and description.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>


<div class="columns">
  <div class="column">
    <p>
